			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Trigger the Ultimatum stage of the last using oe SHA_LastJusticiar_SetState_Ultimatum or the Debug Book&#xD;&#xA;2. Go to -717; -37; -746&#xD;&#xA;3. Enter combat with the rats and kill them" />
